"I'm pleased with the player's application and attitude. These games now aren't about technical ability or tactics, this is about endeavour pride and sacrifice and putting everything into a game.
"At this time of the season, whether you're fighting relegation or trying to get promoted, that's all it's about - heart.
"Results are important not performances, but in the second half I thought we put in an excellent performance."
